---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'About · Yohann Strullu, wedding photographer in Brittany';
const description = 'Yohann Strullu, wedding photographer in Brittany since 2017. Documentary filmmaker (Blue Road, TAN). Wedding Awards 2021, 2022 and 2026.';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
        <h1>Yohann Strullu</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Wedding photographer in Brittany. Pors Poulhan, Plouhinec.
        </p>

        <p>
          Wedding photographer since 2017. I cover around twenty couples a year, no more,
          and I spend the rest of my time traveling, surfing, and being with my son.
        </p>

        <p class="hook">
          I didn't start out in weddings.
        </p>

        <p>
          In 2016, I joined the team of <em>Blue Road</em>, a surf film produced by Alena
          Ehrenbold. I came in to shoot a few behind-the-scenes clips, and ended up filming
          and editing a large part of the film. First award at a festival, first spark.
          <strong>The following year, I founded Black Pixels.</strong>
        </p>

        <p>
          In 2018, I did it again with <em>TAN</em>, a documentary about a Breton surfboard
          shaper, on camera and editing. The film traveled through international festivals
          and won around ten awards, including Best Cinematography at the Surf Film Festival
          in San Diego.
        </p>

        <p>
          What stays with me from TAN is that the film is about our relationship to time.
          And maybe it resonated because we took the time to make it, as if we'd applied
          the film's lessons while shooting it. Or maybe the other way around, and it's
          the way I see things that shaped the film.
        </p>

        <p>
          I try to apply that to my work: do less, but do it well. That's why I never go
          beyond twenty weddings a year. It lets me be present from start to finish on the
          big day, take real care of the editing, and deliver quickly.
        </p>

        <p>
          With weddings, I quickly understood that it's not just about photography. It's a
          real connection with the couple, built before the day itself, and felt in the
          images. It's also a job where you never get bored: you're often alone, true, but
          every couple, every venue, every light is different. Brittany mostly, and
          sometimes elsewhere.
        </p>

        <p class="closing">
          Weddings have given me the life I've always dreamed of.
          And I do my best to give back :)
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-photo">
        <img src="/images/yohann.jpg" alt="Yohann Strullu at a signing session at Cinéma Eckmühl, Penmarc'h" width="2048" height="1152" />
        <p class="photo-caption">Signing session at Cinéma Eckmühl</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-film">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow text-center">The film</p>
      <h2 class="text-center">TAN</h2>
      <p class="film-intro text-center text-muted">
        Directed by Alena Ehrenbold, 2018. Cinematography and editing by me.
      </p>
      <div class="film-embed">
        <iframe
          src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/275924291?h=400ca2b15b&title=0&byline=0&portrait=0"
          loading="lazy"
          allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
          title="TAN · film by Alena Ehrenbold, cinematography & editing by Yohann Strullu"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
      <p class="film-credits text-center text-muted">
        <a href="https://vimeo.com/275924291" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Watch on Vimeo ↗</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-bottom">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="bottom-lines">
        <p><strong>Documentary approach</strong>: few posed shots, lots of stolen moments.</p>
        <p><strong>Color and black &amp; white</strong> as standard.</p>
        <p><strong>Delivery within 2 weeks</strong>, secure online gallery for you and your guests.</p>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 3rem; text-align: center;">
        <a href="/en/contact" class="button">Let's talk about your wedding</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .about-text p { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .hook {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 2rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
  }
  .closing {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--color-accent-dark);
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .about-photo {
    position: sticky;
    top: 6rem;
  }
  .about-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.15);
  }
  .photo-caption {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about-film { background: #1A1A1A; color: #F0EBE0; padding: 5rem 0; }
  .about-film .eyebrow { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .about-film h2 { color: #F0EBE0; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); }
  .film-intro { font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem; color: rgba(240, 235, 224, 0.7); }
  .film-embed {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    background: #000;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }
  .film-embed iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }
  .film-credits { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .film-credits a { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .film-credits a:hover { color: var(--color-bg); }

  .about-bottom { background: white; padding: 5rem 0; }
  .bottom-lines {
    max-width: 580px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .bottom-lines p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .bottom-lines strong { color: var(--color-accent-dark); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .about-photo { position: static; }
  }
</style>
